```

## Deployment

### Docker

```bash
docker build -t <%= serviceNameKebab %> .
docker run -p 8000:8000 -e DATABASE_URL=postgresql://host:5432/db <%= serviceNameKebab %>
```

### Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `DATABASE_URL` | `postgresql://postgres:***@localhost:5432/<%= serviceNameSnake %>` | PostgreSQL connection |
| `DEBUG` | `False` | Debug mode |
| `HOST` | `0.0.0.0` | Server host |
| `PORT` | `8000` | Server port |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | `INFO` | Logging level |
| `SECRET_KEY` | `change-me-in-production` | JWT secret key |

